**IMPLEMENTATION PLAN:**

**Phase 1: Crawler Base Class**
```javascript
class BaseCrawler {
  constructor(type, config) {
    this.type = type;
    this.sources = config.sources;
    this.filters = config.filters;
    this.reportTo = 'ideation-pipeline';
  }

  async scout() { /* Override */ }
  async report(findings) {
    return this.brain.ingest(findings);
  }
}
```

**Phase 2: Specialized Crawlers**
- Extend BaseCrawler for each type
- Configure source APIs
- Define finding schemas

**Phase 3: Pipeline Integration**
